      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLDSTAR MURPHY (3) is a progressive type who recorded his 18th career win last time out (19.15) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can continue on his winning ways. ROSEWOOD REBEL (1) turned in a fair run last time from the squeeze finishing fourth by 1.3 lengths (16.80). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. SHE'S A BULLET (4) was sent out long odds last time but charged out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 3.5 lengths sixth (20.33) over 352m at Q Lakeside. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. FEDERAL EMERAN (8) hit the frame here last start and can sneak into the finish again.",
